### Genfeed API - Lightings Collection Endpoints
### Manage lighting presets for video generation

########################################
# List & Filter Lightings
########################################

### Get All Lightings (Paginated)
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/elements/lightings
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Lightings with Pagination
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/elements/lightings?page=1&limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Active Lightings Only
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/elements/lightings?isActive=true
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Get Default Lightings Only
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/elements/lightings?isDefault=true
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Search Lightings by Name
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/elements/lightings?search=natural
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Sort Lightings
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/elements/lightings?sort=label
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


########################################
# Create, Update, Delete Lightings
########################################

### Create Lighting
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/elements/lightings
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "key": "natural-sunlight",
  "label": "Natural Sunlight",
  "description": "Soft natural sunlight from windows",
  "category": "video",
  "isActive": true,
  "isDefault": false
}


### Update Lighting
PATCH {{apiBaseUrl}}/elements/lightings/{{lightingId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "label": "Natural Daylight",
  "description": "Soft daylight from windows"
}


### Delete Lighting
DELETE {{apiBaseUrl}}/elements/lightings/{{lightingId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

